  <uuid rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">fa19efe5761a4e9e875d57c</uuid>
  <does rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean">true</does>
  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">If you re a registered AOL user you can visit AOL Marketing Preferences to review your marketing preferences and make choices about how your information may be used to provide marketing offers to you Note that these preferences do not apply to communications that are directly related to your registration with AOL or the fulfillment of a specific transaction you have requested for example a service advisory from AOL or an acknowledgment of a purchase order</evidence>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

