<owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="#b0ead7466703462bbf087da:OrganizationalMeasure">
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="#OrganizationalMeasure"/>
  <uuid rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">b0ead7466703462bbf087da</uuid>
  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Our Commitment to Security Although no one can guarantee the security of the information collected and received we do employ a number of safeguards intended to mitigate the risk of unauthorized access or disclosure of this information Examples of the types of safeguards we may provide depending on the circumstances include Storing the data you provide in controlled facilities Using HTTPS encryption when you authenticate i e log into one of our Services which helps prevent unauthorized access to your login credentials Limiting access to personal information to employees who need that access to perform their jobs and Providing company-wide training on privacy and data security</evidence>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

